to see you.

15
00:02:32,819 --> 00:02:36,159
If you got shot, you should show
your face and greet me humbly.

16
00:02:36,830 --> 00:02:39,129
You don't have any manners. Try me.

17
00:02:39,860 --> 00:02:41,729
This time, I'll shoot you
on bare skin.

18
00:02:42,469 --> 00:02:45,139
Not bad. You won.

19
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:47,810
Get down on the floor if you lost.

20
00:02:47,810 --> 00:02:49,939
I wonder why you couldn't
do anything...

21
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:52,639
the day your mom died
in front of your eyes.

22
00:02:54,009 --> 00:02:55,250
Who are you?

23
00:02:58,319 --> 00:03:00,990
Do you even remember the moment
she died?

24
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:04,719
"Mom. Mom."

25
00:03:04,819 --> 00:03:06,259
Mom.

26
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,789
Mom.

27
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,400
Jerk.

28
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:13,500
I remember it clearly.

29
00:03:13,669 --> 00:03:17,169
You were crying your eyes out
as your mom took her last breath.

30
00:03:17,539 --> 00:03:18,840
Do me a favor.

31
00:03:21,139 --> 00:03:22,939
Don't put those handcuffs on.

32
00:03:23,810 --> 00:03:25,110
Just run away.

33
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:28,810
I beg you.

34
00:03:43,259 --> 00:03:46,159
(SWAT)

35
00:03:52,169 --> 00:03:53,569
Don't forget...

36
00:03:54,669 --> 00:03:55,909
my last wish.

37
00:03:56,009 --> 00:03:58,409
- Shut it and stay with me.
- You must find it.

38
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:00,750
At all costs.

39
00:04:04,780 --> 00:04:05,949
The green meadow...

40
00:04:09,689 --> 00:04:10,759
(SWAT)

41
00:04:26,670 --> 00:04:27,939
The green meadow...

42
00:04:29,139 --> 00:04:30,310
The green meadow?

43
00:05:09,410 --> 00:05:11,879
He fell from the rooftop.
Send the men there!

44
00:05:19,089 --> 00:05:20,389
He's in front of the back door.

45
00:05:20,589 --> 00:05:21,990
He's dressed as SWAT.

46
00:05:22,189 --> 00:05:23,290
First floor.

47
00:05:23,490 --> 00:05:25,100
The target is dressed like
one of us.

48
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:26,560
You must all unmask yourselves.

49
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:28,189
We lost both the target
and Det. Dong.

50
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:32,560
I'll take responsibility for this.

51
00:06:32,860 --> 00:06:33,970
"Responsibility"?

52
00:06:34,269 --> 00:06:35,470
Remember this.

53
00:06:35,899 --> 00:06:38,240
No one can take responsibility
for what has happened.

54
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:40,300
Even if both of us get fired,

55
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:42,610
it won't alleviate this situation.

56
00:06:50,579 --> 00:06:54,389
(Episode 11: A Deep Scar)

57
00:06:57,189 --> 00:06:59,720
(TVC Is Righteous and Fair)

58
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:02,160
A suspect the police had been after
is dead.

59
00:07:02,629 --> 00:07:04,430
"Serial killer" and "Eraser".

60
00:07:05,029 --> 00:07:07,269
Make sure these two words are used.

61
00:07:07,370 --> 00:07:09,800
Make use of your connections
with the police, prosecution,

62
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:12,569
and other departments
and blow it up as much as possible.

63
00:07:12,569 --> 00:07:13,670
I want this to make the headlines.

64
00:07:13,970 --> 00:07:15,370
Whom should we target first?

65
00:07:15,610 --> 00:07:17,069
The RIU, of course.

66
00:07:17,509 --> 00:07:19,709
Make sure to mention Dong Baek.

67
00:07:19,879 --> 00:07:23,250
Let our viewers know
that mutants like Dong Baek...

68
00:07:23,579 --> 00:07:25,250
are the problem.

69
00:07:25,980 --> 00:07:28,420
I'm sorry for being late.

70
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:31,459
Hey!

71
00:07:32,620 --> 00:07:34,360
- Yes?
- Who told you to come here?

72
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,459
Are you talking about me?

73
00:07:39,660 --> 00:07:41,670
Did she do what the director
ordered her to do?

74
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:46,269
You're no longer allowed
to enter the newsroom.

75
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:48,939
But...

76
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:52,509
Everyone has been saying that
Det. Dong will be found guilty soon.

77
00:07:52,509 --> 00:07:55,480
- They said he's at rock bottom...
- Who are you to say that?

78
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:58,120
Who are you to make
that decision yourself?

79
00:08:01,089 --> 00:08:02,220
I'm sorry.

80
00:08:02,220 --> 00:08:04,290
Don't you dare show up to work...

81
00:08:04,290 --> 00:08:06,360
unless you've found something good
that'll bring him down.

82
00:08:07,790 --> 00:08:09,290
Don't just stand there, get out.

83
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:43,590
(Captain Koo Kyung Tan)

84
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:50,070
(Captain Koo Kyung Tan)

85
