00:58:09,090 --> 00:58:10,989
died because of you, Dad.

801
00:58:13,900 --> 00:58:15,400
Because of you and me.

802
00:58:18,329 --> 00:58:20,300
Although you can't say anything,

803
00:58:22,469 --> 00:58:24,510
and these people can't hear,

804
00:58:33,050 --> 00:58:34,780
I'm really sorry.

805
00:58:37,590 --> 00:58:39,719
A murderer who always prioritized
his justification...

806
00:58:39,719 --> 00:58:40,989
changed his method of killing.

807
00:58:41,119 --> 00:58:42,860
"An innocent person
will be crucified."

808
00:58:42,860 --> 00:58:44,230
"Instead of the sinner."

809
00:58:44,389 --> 00:58:46,230
His purpose was murder itself.

810
00:58:46,230 --> 00:58:47,730
Cheon Ki Soo is our connection.

811
00:58:47,829 --> 00:58:48,900
Who are you?

812
00:58:49,059 --> 00:58:51,969
A savior who will save
your son's life.

813
00:58:52,070 --> 00:58:54,269
- Cheon Ki Soo disappeared.
- Without a trace.

814
00:58:54,440 --> 00:58:57,210
All I did was chase the Eraser.

815
00:58:57,210 --> 00:58:59,510
- What?
- I saw the scar on his right arm.

816
00:58:59,739 --> 00:59:01,679
- Who is it?
- You were the Eraser.

817
00:59:02,010 --> 00:59:04,480
You were there 20 years ago
in Shimbae!
